u_{jt} + \eta_{jt}| k_{jt}, i_{jt}, k_{j, t - 1}, l_{j, t - 1}, \chi_{jt} = 1\}\ &amp;=  eta_0 +  eta_k k_{jt} + g[\phi^0(k_{j, t - 1}, i_{j, t - 1}) - ( eta_0 +  eta_k k_{j, t - 1})]\ &amp; + \mathbb{E}\{
u_{jt}| k_{jt}, i_{jt}, k_{j, t - 1}, l_{j, t - 1} , \chi_{jt} = 1\}. \end{split} \end{equation}\] and \[ egin{equation} \mathbb{E}\{
